Shader Definition Registry (SDR)

The SDR is a shading-specialized version of the NDR, and provides the following
specialized classes:
* `SdrRegistry`
* `SdrShaderNode`
* `SdrShaderProperty`

For more details on the registry, nodes, or properties, see the base NDR
classes:
* `NdrRegistry`
* `NdrNode`
* `NdrProperty`

For a high-level view of the system and how all the parts work together, see
the overview page for NDR.